+## 18. Confidence Score v2
 
 ```text
 confidence_score = 100 × (
-  0,45 × coverage +
-  0,35 × agreement +
-  0,20 × freshness
+  0.45 × coverage +
+  0.35 × agreement +
+  0.20 × freshness
